159
00:12:27,648 --> 00:12:29,100
Karena Sun Young?

160
00:12:29,100 --> 00:12:31,744
Mereka mengatakan bahwa saya harus meninggalkan Kangseng.

161
00:12:31,744 --> 00:12:34,100
