195
00:14:44,333 --> 00:14:45,888
Sersan Jang Myeong Do,

196
00:14:45,888 --> 00:14:49,400
Sersan Do Hyeong Gu,
Kopral Park Dae Ho, dan...

197
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:53,000
Jaksa Cha Si Young.

198
